Dewey Barto https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dewey_Barto 0 Dewey Barto (June 10, 1896 – January 31, 1973) was best known as half of the comedic and acrobatic dance act, Barto and Mann. He was the father of actress Nancy Walker, known earlier in life as "Nan Barto".
